Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:53.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快回来 钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉不在奈落那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:57.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:07.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 但是四魂之玉突然就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才明明还在奈落体内的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要是钢牙就这么跳进奈落体内的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他脚上的碎片反而会被污染
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,接而被奈落吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:17.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就这样袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬…夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:29.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 去救钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:33.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:36.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看我从内将你毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了 钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 在背后支撑我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人 难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:58.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 法师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在你用风穴将我吸进去之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:05.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你会因为中瘴气之毒而吐血倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,决不让你称心 风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:10.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴 一定要给我撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:25.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢 吸进的只有瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 五雷指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:38.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,后面就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口扩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:48.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着吧 瘦狼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:53.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能那么简单就死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:55.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:04.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙的碎片变黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:05.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:09.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里 奈落的四魂之玉在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:12.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅凭借我的力量无法发现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:15.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是… 四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落把它藏在桔梗体内了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的死魂虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 是现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你是叫我现在射吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,臭丫头 发现了玉的所藏之处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:48.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 死魂虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要夺回四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想把我连玉一同净化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:24.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气的毒幕把玉污染了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:33.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,同玉一起吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:42.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的灵力在破坏着奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,脚挣脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我的碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:01.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在玉之内桔梗的灵力和奈落的邪气在对抗着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:02.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 看得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落正在垂死挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:11.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,邪气在扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:19.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:30.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 最后一块碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,守护…琥珀的光…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:38.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是只有你才能做得到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:40.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事对我而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:46.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 不是说用那弓箭就能净化你的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就能拯救你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底有没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 你临死之时就会知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片只剩下一块了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:17.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好好期待吧 没有桔梗的你该怎么战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:19.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗败给了我的邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:31.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不能乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:52.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我非回去不可 桔梗大人的气息变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道大人现在到底是怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:59.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,话说在前头 别指望杀生丸大人会带你回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托他也不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,风的气息变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗小姐 发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:12.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们 差不多该回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:16.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,夕阳红得像火一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真美丽啊 枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:28.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是鲜血的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我 没能救得了桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:49.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们单独待一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 桔梗 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你拯救了我早已污浊的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:26.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你经历了这样长久的痛苦往事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没有那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:34.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:53.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在桔梗大人变成那样之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来有机会用风穴消灭掉奈落的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:57.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我因为惧怕着死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:03.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而犹豫着不敢打开风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明明桔梗小姐还救过我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:08.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:15.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 是为了我 才要你留在人世的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:20.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨过桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,恨她想把弟弟的生命 把维系琥珀生命的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,当成打倒奈落的工具来使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:32.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 当我看到她救了钢牙时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:38.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她一定是为了保护琥珀而战斗着的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经失去了四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:46.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗 桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么也没能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我有更强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:02.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能更早一点赶到的话 桔梗她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:04.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:08.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看来真的很不想让桔梗和犬夜叉再会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他还是及时赶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得吗 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:25.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们被奈落挑拨而决裂之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:29.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 要用四魂之玉变成人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果变成人类 那桔梗你会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我是玉的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果玉不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会变成普通的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:48.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我想变成人类和你一起生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于…变成普通的女人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:59.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 你是我有生以来第一个喜欢上的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:06.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此 我还是什么都没能为你做到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:14.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你用那种表情哭呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:19.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 我…我没能救得了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你…赶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:27.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这就足够了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:29.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:40.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:49.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这些光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:16.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:19.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是在与我们告别一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:39.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗说让我们别再悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:50.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,说她会永远守护着我们

